                    "value": "<p>@Template[type:emanation|distance:15]{15 feet} @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.bestiary-ability-glossary-srd.Item.Aura]</p>\n<hr />\n<p>The fuming sludge constantly emits incendiary smoke that creates @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Concealed]{Concealment} around it. The smoke doesn't impair the fuming sludge's chemical sense. A creature that enters the aura or begins its turn in the aura becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (@Check[type:fortitude|dc:25] negates) and cannot recover from @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Persistent Damage]{Persistent Fire Damage} for 1 round. It is then temporarily immune to the sickening effect of the smoldering haze for 1 minute.</p>\n<p>A creature that is currently holding its breath, that doesn't need to breathe, or that's immune to poison is immune to the aura's sickened effect but not the concealment or inability to recover from persistent fire damage.</p>"
